      "content": "i get what you mean about the side effects but i feel like the melatonin is pretty mild compared to the ambien. most people take melatonin every night without any issues. if i just take a small amount of the melatonin along with my prescribed ambien dose, it shouldn't be too bad, right? i just really can't afford to be this tired at work tomorrow.",
